room_title: Escape room "The Fallout Room" by Clueology Rooms in Fort Collins
room_address: 907 N Van Buren Ave #150 Loveland, CO 80537
room_description: Your group is taking a hike in the Colorado mountains when a storm rolls in. You stumble upon a hidden cabin deep in the woods. This is no ordinary cabin: inside lies an intricate web of secret passageways, stolen government files and a robot on patrol! You must locate the super drive and escape while there's still time!
